*Come Meet and Network with Other Professionals at Venue in Framingham!  There are 87 RSVP's Right Now!*
Bring some business cards, a smile, and a professional attitude because it's time to make some valuable new business contacts as we move into 2013.
Dress code is "business casual", professional, yet comfortable.
(No Cover Charge, Appetizers, and Plenty of Parking at Great Location on Rte 9)
